                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5028" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">BL-0026</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11554 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">亲爱的投资人，你在和谁对赌？—华工公司对赌案</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dear investors, who are you gambling against?: the Huagong VAM case</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨宏玲，邹艳，张亚莉，王艳平</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华工公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">对赌协议；资本维持原则；股份回购；目标公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">the Valuation Adjustment Mechanism Agreement, the doctrine of capital maintenance, share repurchase, target company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在“对赌第一案”——海富案之后的2019年，法院对类似的华工案却做出了不同的判决，华工案由此成为当年投资界影响最大的案件之一。案中原告华工公司与增资的目标公司及其股东签订了对赌协议，该协议约定承担股份回购义务的主体是目标公司，股东只承担配合回购的义务。法院最终判决华工公司与目标公司之间的回购型对赌协议有效，此认定与海富案中确立的原则显然不同，由此引发了法律界和投资界的高度关注。本案例旨在引导学生在学习理解公司法中资本维持原则的基础上，进一步思考公司股份回购义务的履行对债权人利益保护的影响。同时在分析对赌协议效力的过程中，让学生体会资本市场的复杂和多变，以及公司法在保护债权人和股东利益之间的平衡。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After the case of Haifu Investment Co., Ltd., the first VAM-related case, the Court made different judgments on the case of Huagong in 2019 despite its similarities to that of Haifu. Huagong Case consequently became one of the most influential cases in the investment circles that year. In this case, the plaintiff, Huagong, signed a VAM agreement with the investee and its shareholders. The agreement stipulates that the investee is the party to bear the liability of share repurchase while the shareholders only have the obligation to cooperate. The Court finally adjudicated that the VAM agreement with share repurchase terms agreed upon by Huagong and the investee was valid. This judgment is obviously different from the principles established in the Haifu case. The inconsistency has aroused great concern amongst the legal and investment circles. The case aims to guide students to reflect on the impact of the company&#39;s fulfillment of its liability of repurchase on the protection of creditors’ interests based on thorough understanding of the doctrines of capital maintenance under the Company Law. At the same time, in analysis of the validity of the VAM agreement, students should learn to realize the complexity and variation of the capital market, and the balance between the protection of creditors and shareholders’ interests under the Company Law.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商法》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">专利对于新创企业的重要性、专利战的复杂性、专利战略与市场战略协同配合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
